{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An Everyday Story is a story-driven puzzle platformer with a heartfelt twist. A man holds dear three little trinkets, each representing his bond with a loved one... play as a Tin Soldier, a Bat Origami and a Wooden Boat through an adventure to regain lost memories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192920/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__11_.gif?t=1727705447\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What do you think happens when our dreams become so real to stain our reality?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the melancholy of life, needings and wishes, forgiveness, memories, nostalgia, and unravel the backstory of the main protagonist's family. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192920/extras/Narrativa.gif?t=1727705447\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Become agile and swift as the Bat Origami and use the tin soldier's unique equipment to navigate dangerous environments</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As humans travel throughout their lives, so do their trinkets! Explore multiple locations scattered across the globe, each filled by platforming action. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192920/extras/Action.gif?t=1727705447\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Use your cunning to resolve puzzles with the mighty wooden boat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Resolve environmental puzzles and use your strengths to overcome everyday obstacles, or ram through them, you have the power... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192920/extras/WoodenBoatMistery.gif?t=1727705447\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Size matters!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">... but be careful! Being tiny is a double-edged sword: you can slip through narrow passages and avoid most dangers... but you are also very delicate, and anything can stomp you at any time! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192920/extras/deathMontage.gif?t=1727705447\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A new reality</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to delve into your deepest nightmares? Sometimes, memories and fears can manifest in, let's say, very colourful and dangerous ways. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192920/extras/SoldierNightmare.gif?t=1727705447\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192920/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727705447","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192920/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1727705447","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192920/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727705447","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2192920/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727705447","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2466480,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An Everyday Story is a story-driven puzzle platformer with a heartfelt twist. A man holds dear three little trinkets, each representing his bond with a loved one... play as a Tin Soldier, a Bat Origami and a Wooden Boat through an adventure to regain lost memories. </p><p c